---
// Offers.astro — What Breakthru Offers: coaching approach and outcomes in card grid
---

<section id="offers" class="py-24 bg-base-200">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">

    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50 mb-2">What Breakthru Offers</p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold max-w-xl mx-auto leading-tight">
        The coaching approach and outcomes clients can expect
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-70">
        Two sentences framing the Breakthru method: sustainable, evidence-backed, built around the individual — whether a complete beginner or a competitive athlete.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Offering cards — 3 col desktop, 1 col mobile -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="card card-border">
        <div class="card-body">
          <!-- Icon placeholder -->
          <div class="skeleton w-10 h-10 mb-4 rounded-lg"></div>
          <h3 class="card-title">Personalised Programming</h3>
          <p>
            2–3 sentences describing how training plans are built around the individual client's starting point, goals, schedule, and lifestyle — not a generic template.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="card card-border">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="skeleton w-10 h-10 mb-4 rounded-lg"></div>
          <h3 class="card-title">Mindset and Habit Coaching</h3>
          <p>
            2–3 sentences on the mindset and behaviour-change side of Breakthru — how Myer addresses confidence, consistency, and the mental side of transformation alongside the physical work.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="card card-border">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="skeleton w-10 h-10 mb-4 rounded-lg"></div>
          <h3 class="card-title">Strength and Body Transformation</h3>
          <p>
            2–3 sentences on the physical outcomes: building real, lasting strength, improving body composition, and developing fitness that holds up beyond the programme.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4 -->
      <div class="card card-border">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="skeleton w-10 h-10 mb-4 rounded-lg"></div>
          <h3 class="card-title">100% Online Delivery</h3>
          <p>
            2–3 sentences explaining the online-only model — how it works, what the client receives week to week, and why location is never a barrier to getting started.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 5 -->
      <div class="card card-border">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="skeleton w-10 h-10 mb-4 rounded-lg"></div>
          <h3 class="card-title">For All Fitness Levels</h3>
          <p>
            2–3 sentences making explicit that Breakthru is not only for advanced athletes — complete beginners are welcome and the approach scales from day one to elite marginal gains.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 6 -->
      <div class="card card-border">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="skeleton w-10 h-10 mb-4 rounded-lg"></div>
          <h3 class="card-title">No Quick Fixes</h3>
          <p>
            2–3 sentences on the Breakthru philosophy of rejecting extreme measures — why Myer coaches for sustainable long-term results rather than short-term performance that doesn't last.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Section CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <a href="#qualify" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Apply to Work With Myer</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
